title: 049 - Calypso Is DEAD
description: On today's show, the guys come to the realization that Connor has potentially never actually eaten at a buffet before, they check in with their Australian correspondents The Boobz Brothers, go through some #PodFacts, answer a couple of listener questions involving choosing one snack, movie, and TV show to watch for the rest of their lives, what makes for a good bartender, and Connor unfortunately tells the tale of how Calypso is likely dead after an incredible three months together. Don't forget to send your questions to @ThePodPMI on Instagram and Twitter, and stay safe out there. Enjoy.
